data.description: This home is perfect for a large family boasting 4 Large bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. Plenty of room for everyone to have their own space with 2 living rooms, breakfast nook, office space, dining room, and a large screened back porch for entertaining. Completely fenced and ready for your pets. Roof 2016, New AC 2023, New Drain field 2023, Sunken above ground pool with a 7 ft deep end. Completely fenced with a large covered shelter and shed.
